Programs
1) Non-parameterized method that returns your name
class Test {

    String getName() {

        return "Gauransh Kate";
    }

    public static void main(String[] args) {

        Test t = new Test();

        System.out.println(t.getName());

    }
}
Output
Gauransh Kate
